learning_outcomes.en:
Successful graduate of the course understands the effects of technological developments in the design of public services.
Successful graduate of the course:
* Understands the effects of technological developments in the design of public services;
* Can see the possibilities of applying technologies to solve complex problems in specific areas of the public sector;
* Has an overview of various challenges and risks of digital solutions;
* Can estimate the cost of investment in the creation of digital services.

learning_outcomes.et:
Kursuse edukalt läbinu: 
* saab aru tehnoloogiliste arengute mõjudest avaliku sektori teenuste kujundamises; 
* oskab näha tehnoloogiate rakendamise võimalusi keeruliste probleemide lahendamiseks spetsiifilistes avaliku sektori valdkondades; 
* omab ülevaadet erinevatest digilahenduste väljakutsetest ja riskidest;   
* suudab hinnata digitaalsete teenuste loomise investeeringute maksumust.
